items.title: Million-year-old skull could rewrite human evolution timeline
items.description: The findings have the potential to resolve the longstanding "Muddle in the Middle" of human evolution, researchers said.

items.title: Trump heads to first day of Ryder Cup to boost U.S. team
items.description: President Trump is heading to New York to attend the first day of the 45th Ryder Cup as the best U.S. golfers take on the best from Europe.

items.title: Coast Guard releases image of alleged drug boat on fire after seizures
items.description: The Coast Guard says it seized nearly 30,000 pounds of cocaine from alleged drug boats in recent weeks.

items.title: ICE officer relieved of duties after videos show him shoving woman to ground
items.description: An ICE officer who was captured on video pushing a woman to the ground outside an immigration court in New York City has been relieved of his duties.
